                  <h2>
                    &nbsp;
                  </h2>
                  <h4>
                    The National Gallery of Canada (NGC) offers a wealth of images to researchers, publishers and others seeking to visually enhance their projects and products.<br />
                    <br />
                    Photographic reproductions of many works of art in the permanent collection are available for use in books, journals, newspapers, theses, on websites, cards, posters, CDs, and other merchandise.<br />
                    <a href="/en/image-reproduction/index.php">Learn more</a>
